'''Andy Mangels''' (born [[December 2]], [[1960s#1966|1966]])<ref name="bday" /> is the [[Wikipedia:Americans|American]]<ref name="American" /> author of the [[1995]] reference book ''[[The Essential Guide to Characters]]'',<ref name="TEGTC">''[[The Essential Guide to Characters]]''</ref> the script author of the [[1996]] [[Dark Horse Comics]] one-shot ''[[Boba Fett: Twin Engines of Destruction]]'',<ref name="Twin Engines">''[[Boba Fett: Twin Engines of Destruction]]''</ref> and the writer of the feature "[[Just Who Is Boba Fett?]]" in the [[1998]] one-shot magazine ''[[Star Wars: Boba Fett]]''.<ref name="Star Wars: Boba Fett">"[[Just Who Is Boba Fett?]]"&mdash;''[[Star Wars: Boba Fett]]''</ref>

